pe of certificates can be\ngeneralized to other discrete dynamical systems, where proofs involve large\ncase enumerations as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2015 18:24:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 11:43:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2018 16:10:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-16"}
