uantum level, thus the subtraction function must depend on the dilaton only.\nThe method is useful in models where preserving scale symmetry at quantum level\nis important.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2015 20:42:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 17:39:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2015 20:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2016 21:18:45 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2016 20:37:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-06"}
